<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator.ClearAllPlugins" Title="ClearAllPlugins method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.RenderPluginEnumerator">RenderPluginEnumerator</PageRef> ->
    ClearAllPlugins
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ClearAllPlugins</TypeRef> method removes every loaded plugin record and releases the module handles owned by the enumerator.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Warning">
      <Paragraph>
        Only call this after all objects created from the loaded plugins have been destroyed, unless another module handle is keeping the plugin loaded.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void ClearAllPlugins();]]></Code>
  </Section>
